Finnish Security Guards Get Wage Hikes, Averts Strikes, YLE Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-03-02T06:23:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/finnish-security-guards-get-wage-hikes-averts-strikes-yle-says.html
Finnish security guards won wage
increases of as much as 2.8 percent over two years, averting
strikes planned for today and next week, state-owned broadcaster
YLE reported today, citing Jyrki Sinkkonen, who is in charge of
negotiations at Service Union United PAM.  Click here for web link in Finnish  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
